  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1957230/extras/24a19599e72c25402036bc338cc2851b.poster.avif?t=1696791901\" width=600 height=476 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1957230/extras/24a19599e72c25402036bc338cc2851b.webm?t=1696791901\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1957230/extras/24a19599e72c25402036bc338cc2851b.mp4?t=1696791901\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1957230/extras/f1a9a57a614fb1433e87162d5798d5e9.webp?t=1696791901\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1957230/extras/f1a9a57a614fb1433e87162d5798d5e9.poster.avif?t=1696791901\" class=\"bb_img\" width=616 height=100 /></picture></span><br><i>Salary : €9 - €11 an hour<br><br>Become a member of The Month, a rural market store that provides for local communities. Staff here provide a friendly shopping experience for customers, answer questions and offer suggestions. Responsibilities may include :<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Working to accomplish goals<br></li><li>Operating the cash register in a fun and efficient manner<br></li><li>Stocking shelves<br></li><li>Cleaning the store and general maintenance<br></li><li>Helping customers find their favorite products<br></li><li>You'll learn a lot. You're not stuck doing one task here. Each Crew Member contributes to creating a WOW customer experience by participating in all aspects of the job.</li></ul><br>If you have a passion for money, we'd love to meet you. We can teach you the rest.<br>The Month is an equal opportunity employer and is committed to hiring damn near anyone.</i><br><br>                     <i>NOTE : Must have a flexible schedule.</i><br>                                                 - <i>Manger</i><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1957230/extras/1982346744f4cf61f474ca1d068f1ff5.webp?t=1696791901\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1957230/extras/1982346744f4cf61f474ca1d068f1ff5.poster.avif?t=1696791901\" class=\"bb_img\" width=616 height=100 /></picture></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>First person exploration with unique and unsettling environments.<br></li><li>Play with Mouse & Keyboard or Controller.<br></li><li>Retro-inspired graphics.<br></li><li>Interactable and readable objects at every corner.<br></li><li>Multiple endings and modes.</li></ul><br><br><strong>Employee of the Month contains mature themes and scenes of explicit violence, gore and bad language.</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1957230/extras/36dc7302868093184e54fde27581c64a.poster.avif?t=1696791901\" width=616 height=462 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1957230/extras/36dc7302868093184e54fde27581c64a.webm?t=1696791901\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1957230/extras/36dc7302868093184e54fde27581c64a.mp4?t=1696791901\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
